## Troubleshooting
### Powershell & Scripts
If you see `File ... cannot be loaded because running scripts is disabled`, run:
`Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Scope CurrentUser`

### AI Service Connection Refused
Ensure the Python service is running on port 5001:
```cmd
cd shubkar/ai-budget-assistant
pip install -r requirements.txt
python app.py
```
